(high-pitched tone)
<i>I have.... memor... memor...</i>

38
00:02:14,130 --> 00:02:16,864
(grinding, beeping)

39
00:02:16,899 --> 00:02:19,033
(gentle piano playing)

40
00:02:19,068 --> 00:02:21,969
(high-pitched):
Still love you, Homar.

41
00:02:22,004 --> 00:02:25,739
(high-pitched, distorted):
We are happy family.

42
